lign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udaurion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daurion</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/14/01 12:57:52 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www-edlab.cs.umass.edu/~akielbas/jbravo0.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: They need to see the damage we Wizzy's do!</span><hr size=1> this has been brought up many times, personally i'm ok with it being one way or another.<br>
